<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1944-03-21T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1944-03-21T00:00:00-05:00" n="3" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d3">
                        <note rend="inline" type="source">Roosevelt Papers: Telegram</note>
                        <head><hi rend="italic">Prime Minister <persName type="from">Churchill</persName> to President <persName type="to">Roosevelt</persName></hi><note n="1" xml:id="d3fn1">Sent by the
                                United States Military Attaché, London, via Army
                            channels.</note></head>
                        <opener>
                            <seg rendition="#left"><hi rend="smallcaps">most secret</hi></seg>
                            <dateline rendition="#right"><placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">London</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1944-03-21">21 March 1944</date>.</dateline>
                        </opener>
                        <p>Prime Minister to President Roosevelt. Number 629 most secret and
                            personal. Your 506.<note n="2" xml:id="d3fn2"><hi rend="italic">Supra.</hi></note></p>
                        <list>
                            <label>1.</label>
                            <item>I am indeed grieved and trust rest will do you good.</item>
                            <label>2.</label>
                            <item>I do not think the staff meeting worthwhile without our being
                                there.</item>
                            <label>3.</label>
                            <item>I hope you are still planning your visit here for the great
                                    event<note n="3" xml:id="d3fn3">The Allied invasion of Normandy
                                        (<gloss target="#t_Overlord1"><hi rend="smallcaps">Overlord</hi></gloss>).</note> after you are fully
                                recovered.</item>
                        </list>
                    </div>
                    </body></text></TEI>